</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utalicmoore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talic Moore</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <b>knows that Warriors are Superior</b><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/16/01 10:09:51 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.darkageofcamelot.com/concept/elfw.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapons Training</span><hr size=1> Wait, I'm confused. You stopped worrying about 1hs, 1hb, and piercing because of your staff... but you will always duel wield? *scratches his head in bewilderment* I need a drink... <p>Talic Asaria Moore--
